                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210606-72-off416 t18210606-72-cd417"></join>, one liquor stand, value 1 l.; three decanters, value 1 l.; one set of castors and stand, value 1 l., and one snuff-box, value 7 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18210606-72-victim913" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
